long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Play the classic "Run Dino 🦖" game right from your Chrome extension! Enjoy endless dino running action without any blockers. 🏃‍♂️💨

How to Play: 🦖🦖🦖

1. Start the Game: Press the Spacebar to launch "Run Dino."
2. Jump Over Obstacles: Press the Spacebar to make the dino jump over obstacles like cacti and birds.
3. Dino Dash: Keep running as far as you can while avoiding obstacles to achieve the highest score.
4. Collect Points: The longer you run, the higher your score! Aim for new high scores with each run.

🌟 Play more games on the top-left menu for more fun and exciting adventures!
